# Backend modules (redis, postgres, ipc_encrypted, ws) are bundled
# separately via the [lib.backends] profile in cyrius.cyml — see
# dist/majra-backends.cyr. Consumers who don't need network transports
# pull dist/majra.cyr and get the lean core engine. Tests run via
# tests/test_backends.tcyr and tests/test_live.tcyr.

# =============================================================================
# Tests
